quran[27]{c,v,t}:
  10,26,"Bamwe bagize ineza bazoronswa ineza zabo n’umusesekara, n’inkungugu ntizizopfuka amaso yabo, kandi ntihazoboneka ibimaramare kuribo, abo nibo bantu bo mw’ijuru bazobayo mu buzima bwabo bwose"
  10,27,"Nabamwe bagize ibikorwa bibi, impembo y’ivyo bikorwa bibi nink’akarorero kavyo nyene, n’ibimaramare bizobashikira, kandi ntibazoba bafise uwushobora kubakingira n’ibihano vy’Imana, rero amaso yabo azoba afutswe n’ibimanyu vy’ijoro vy’umwijima muniniya, rero abo nibo bantu bo mumuriro udahera, ariho bazobayo mubuzima bwamisi yose"
  10,28,"N‘umusi tuzobegeranya bose hanyuma tubabwire bamwe bagereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu duti:- nimuhagarare kuruhande rwanyu hamwe nabamwe mwagereranije kuba basomambike banyu b’Imana hanyuma tubashire kuruhande rwabo, abo bagereranije abandi n’Imana bazovuga bati:- mwebwe ntimwamye mudusenga twebwe"
  10,29,"Imana yonyene irahagije kuba ariyo cabona kiri hagati yacu na mwebwe, mu vy’ukuri twebwe ntamakuru y’amasengesho yanyu twari tuzi"
  10,30,"Iyo umuntu wese yomenya ivyo yagize vyose, hanyuma bakazosubizwa ku Mana yabo, ariwe Muremyi wabo w’ukuri, hanyuma hakazozimangana bimwe bahora badukana navyo"
  10,31,"Vuga uti:- ni nde abaha imfashanyo ivuye mw’ijuru no kw’isi? Canke ni nde nyene amatwi n’amaso yanyu, kandi ni nde akura umuntu muzima mubasandavye nugukura uwasandavye mu bantu bazima? None ni nde agira ibi vyose? Nabo bazovuga bati:- n’Imana, rero wewe vuga uti:- mbega mwebwe ntimutinya"
  10,32,"Iyo niyo Mana Umuremyi wanyu w’ukuri, none n’ikihe kintu kiriho inyuma y’ukuri atari ubuzimire gusa, none mwebwe muhindukizwa hehe"
  10,33,"Uku niko ijambo ry’Umuremyi wawe rizobashikira bamwe biyonkoye, yuko batazo kwemera"
  10,34,"Vuga uti:- mbega hariho umwe muribo mugereranya n’Imana yatanguje kurema ibiremwa hanyuma ikazobigarura vuga uti:- n’Imana niyo yatanguje kurema ibiremwa vyose hanyuma niyo izo bigarura, none muhindurirwa hehe"
  10,35,"Vuga uti:- mbega hari muri abo mugereranya n’Imana ibarongora m’ukuri? Vuga uti:- Imana niyo irongora abantu m’ukuri, rero uwurongora abantu m’ukuri siwe ategerezwa cane gukurikirwa canke umwe atarongotse atari uwurongowe, mbega mubaye gute? None mutegeka gute"
  10,36,"Benshi muribo ntibakurikira ibintu n’ibindi atari amakenga gusa, nayo amakenga ntaco amaze imbere y’ukuri n’ikintu na gitoyi, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ibintu vyose mugira"
  10,37,"Ntibishoboka yuko iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu yoba yaranditswe kubinyoma kandi itavuye ku Mana, ahubwo n’amajambo yavuye ku Mana yemeza ivyabaye imbere yaho, kandi n’amajambo y’ibitabu vy’akahise, rero ntamakenga arimwo kandi n’amajambo yavuye kumuremyi w’abantu bose"
  10,38,"Mbega nibo bavuga yuko ariwe yayiyandikiye, vuga uti:- nimuzane kimwe mugisomwa kimeze nk’iki gisomwa, hanyuma muhamagare abo mushoboye kuronka dukuye mwo Imana yonyene gusa, nimwaba mwebwe muvugisha ukuri kwama"
  10,39,"Ahubwo barahakanye muvyo batazi vy’ukuri nuko kuri ntikwari bwabashikire namba haba k’ububeshi bwabo canke k’ukuri kwabo, uku rero niko kwabaye uguhahana kwababayeko imbere yabo, rero nimugende murabe amaherezo yabo bantu bahemukiye imitima yabo"
  10,40,"No muribo harimwo abemera iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu, n’abandi muribo batayemera, n’Umuremyi wawe arazi neza abononyi"
  10,41,"Nibabandanya n’uguhakana wewe n’uvuge uti:- Jewe ndafise ibikorwa vyanje namwe murafise ibikorwa vyanyu, mwebwe muri kure nivyo nkora, nanje ndikure yivyo mwebwe mukora"
  10,42,"Hari bamwe muribo bakwumviriza, rero woshobora kubumvisha abatumva naho badashaka gutegera"
  10,43,Harimwo bamwe muribo bakwitegereza n’amaso yabo mbega woshobora kurongora impumyi nabo badashaka kubona
  10,44,"Mu vy’ukuri Imana ntihemukira abantu bayo kukintu icarico cose, mugabo abantu nibo bahemukira imitima yabo"
  10,45,"N’umusi izobegerenya nkakumwe batabayeho ng’aha kw’Isi atari isaha imwe yonyene gusa y’umutaga, niho bazomenyana mu vy’ukuri abazohomba muri bamwe bahakanye yuko kutazohura n’Imana yabo kandi ntibazoba mubarongoka"
  10,46,"Nitwakwereka bimwe muvyo tubatuza canke tukwishe, ingaruka yabo izoba iwacu hanyuma Imana niyo cabona civyo bagira vyose"
  10,47,"N’abantu bose bamye bafise intumwa y’Imana, rero mugihe hashika intumwa yabo nuguciribwa urubanza ruri hagati yabo rw’ukuri nabo badahemukiwe"
  10,48,"Nabo bavuga bati:- niryari iryo sango rizobera nimwaba muvugisha ukuri"
  10,49,"Vuga uti:- ntaco ntunze kubera umutima wanje haba kucongirira inabi canke icongirira ineza mugabo Imana ibishatse abantu bose barafise ikiringo cabo kigeze ntikibatebesha n’isaha n’imwe canke ngo babe imbere yaco"
  10,50,"Vuga uti:- mubona gute nkiyo mwoshikirwa nivyo bihano vy’Imana mw’ijoro canke k’umurango, none nikuki bamwe bafise ibicumuro bahakana yuko vyobashikira ningoga na ningoga"
  10,51,Bimaze kuba niho muzo kwemera? Mbega ubu niho mwemera kandi namwe mwamye mubihimiriza ngo bibe
  10,52,"Hanyuma abahemukiye imitima yabo bazobabwira bati:- nimuhonje ibihano bizobagumako ataco muzorihwa, atari kuvyo mwahora mugira"